Migraines- Apply to where it hurts.  Second step: apply to your sternum.  Many of those who experience migraines also feel tenderness or numbness at the sternum.  Releasing the energy there and allowing the shoulder blade energy to open can significantly reduce the occurrence of migraines.  We have had wonderful feedback of migraines falling away within minutes of applying Red Yeti.  

Use the Mustard Bath Treatment for full body pain and releasing of core pain issues.
